abstract: >-
  Reliability for LLM agents through enforcement, not model size — an
  Agent-Contract-Kernel (schema-as-single-source-of-truth, validate→reask→retry)
  paired with a fail-closed orchestration engine. Model-agnostic: runs against any
  OpenAI-compatible endpoint.
